Dialogs.Dialog: Hmm...？ Is it boring to be with Rinko？
Then Rinko will also keep silent, okay？
So quiet... Are you acting like an emo guy？
Are you in a bad mood？
Hey... Is it okay that we get closer？
Hey... Are you thinking that we should hold hands？
It's common for lovers to hold hands, isn't it...？
You know... Rinko's hand feels lonely now.
Are you in the mood for this？
This is... quite embarrassing. ...Are you angry？
Do you think we look like lovers？
We sure look like lovers when we do this.
My hand isn't the only thing that gets warm.
People with cold hands have warm hearts, you know？
Then you mean Rinko has cold heart？
I didn't mean it that way...
Actually, Rinko is trying to be more honest, you know...？
Ah！ Don't let go of my hand！
Somehow, when you do this, it feels like you really care about Rinko.
What？ Why are you squirming like that？
For something like this, why do you have to ask！？
Don't you feel embarrassed doing this？
Will you feel bad if a girl holds your hand...？
Not at all！ I'll be very happy with it.
Really？ Then let me hold your hand.
It feels nice when we walk hand in hand like this.
Well, humming a catchy love song isn't always bad. Anyway, I would limit it to just an occasion like this.
If Rinko holds your hand, will you be happy？
Okay. We feel the same... Next time, Rinko will be the one holding your hand.
Okay, I'll try to remember this.
What do you think if our hands were glued and we had to hold hands all the time？
...How are we gonna use the bathroom then？
Y-You idiot！ Is that the only thing you can think of？ You pervert dirty old man！
Do we look like lovers now？
Then do we look like a married couple now？
Um, maybe 5 years later, we will.
Hehe... Five years？ And we'll never be apart, right？
How many girls have you ever held hands like this？
Let me think... Ten, maybe... No, there are more than that...
There is a girl who lives next door, and then my cousin, and then...
What...？ You seem to be quite popular, huh！？
Why do lovers have to hold hands？ If they get lost, can't they go home by themselves？
Well, why does ▲小早川＊▲ want to hold hands, then？
Look at your smiling face. Does Rinko's face also look like that？
Yeah, we both look the same.
We don't need to hold hands anymore...
Don't ever forget it again, okay？
We always go by that house when we walk this way. It looks expensive.
Yeah. The garden looks nice as well. It's such a nice house.
The maintenance cost would be high. It would require a lot of money and effort. It must be troublesome.
But if we could live together in that house, it would be nice. If it's our own house, I wouldn't mind working hard.
That's true... Hey, why did you decide that we'd live together...？ Geez...
Yeah. But it's difficult to have your own house nowadays.
Hmm？ So you want to have your own house？
Yeah, it'll be our love nest. We'll build it together. Then we'll have a baby and the 3 of us will live there together.
...Well, that's the future. Rinko still doesn't know...
Ah, that mansion is very stylish.
Stylish...？ You mean that Western style building？ I noticed that you looked at it every time we walked by it. You like it？
No, no. I wonder if people can live there. It's like an object of art that you can only appreciate by watching.
Really？ But it looks nice. I want to try living there, at least.
I see. If you're gonna live there alone, I won't stop you...
Eh？ It's not out of business yet.
That's not it. It's just that apartment. I think they've been trying to find tenants for ages.
Doesn't it look nice？ If we live there, we can spend time together or maybe snuggle up to each other.
You're dreaming too far. And for something like that, we can do it no matter where we live.
That house with a cracked window... Does anyone live there？
I don't know. It seems like it was abandoned if you think about it. Maybe the owner had passed away.
It's sad that the house was left behind like that...
...It's okay. If it's us, something like that would never happen...
Yeah... You're right... Shall we get going？
Ah, over there... There are some birds on the wall.
Ah, they are cuddling up. They might be given the "Best Couple" award.
What？ Do birds have that kind of award？
Well, that award should be given out no matter if you're a human or bird.
Really？ Who are the best couple in human world, then？
...Ah, there are a lot of crows.
Crows, huh...？ I feel uneasy seeing so many crows gathering around like that.
There are a lot of crows around here. I see them all the time.
...Really？ But I don't feel good seeing them. Let's hurry and get out of here.
It's fine... Just don't leave me here alone.
Ah, a cat... Yeah, it's such a beautiful cat.
Like, there are beautiful girls or handsome guys, right？ That cat's face makes her look smart and beautiful.
All cats look the same to me.
If you can't even pay attention to a cat's face, it's difficult for Rinko to talk with you, okay？
Ah, a dog. Look, it's over there.
A Doberman, I think. It was tied with a chain, so I think it's okay.
I'm scared of it but I think it'd be cool to have one as a pet... Too bad I live in an apartment...
It keeps barking at us. Let's get going.
Are you using that as an excuse to hold my hand？ Hmm.
Hey, that's... Someone is taking a meerkat for a walk...
I don't know. I think meerkat is a wild animal, so maybe you need to take it for a walk so it won't get stressed.
I see. I should take you for a walk, too, so that you won't get stressed.
Well, a cloud that looked like you has just crumbled.
A cloud that looked like me...？ You saw something like that？
I don't believe in premonition, but if you disappeared in front of my eyes like that, I'd be mad.
A shooting star？ That can't be. Not at this hour.
Yeah. I didn't make a wish, but I believe that something good will happen.
Smell？ No, I don't smell anything.
I know. You're too dumb to sense that.
It's probably the smell of dinner from a house...
Well... Seems like it's about to rain.
Yeah, the air is getting humid.
Yeah, you're right. Do you have an umbrella？
No. Let's hurry up before it starts raining.
Oh no, something got in my eyes....
No, I'm not okay... Ah, geez.
Over there. There's a junior high couple. They're holding hands.
They look happy. We shouldn't lose to them. Let's hold hands.
I didn't mean it that way. When I was their age, I would have never imagined that I'd have a day like this.
Ah, that grandpa and grandma are holding hands...
I see. Age doesn't matter, then.
Well, yeah. Even after they've grown old, their love hasn't changed.
They're an example that we should follow.
Eh？ Did you just walk down that road？
...I've been walking next to you this whole time.
Right. But that guy looked exactly like you.
Don't mix me up with someone else. That's weird.
But, could that be... your imposter？
Wow, she has a nice body！
Can you not react like that？ I'm the only one you should look at.
But since ▲小早川＊▲ looked at her, I couldn't help looking at her, too.
But there's someone here you shouldn't take your eyes off of. Don't you understand？
Why was that girl in a hurry like that？
Maybe she's on her way to meet a friend. She looked like a grade schooler.
Hey, hey, did you see that？ That yellow bicycle was so cute.
The one that just went by？ That design seems to be suited to the stone-paved streets in Europe.
It's nice... I want one, too...
No, even if you want it, it's not quite possible. That brand is very expensive.
I see... But I really like it.
Ah, that motorbike looks like the one on the CD jacket.
It's a popular motorbike that's imported. That one's very expensive.
Hmm. It looks really different from the ones made in Japan.
Do you like it？ I'll always keep the back seat available for ▲小早川＊▲ then.
You'd better get a driver's license before saying that.
Hey, there's a car coming this way. Come here and walk closer to me.
By the way, I think a big car is more convenient than a small one.
Really？ But the gas and insurance costs would be expensive. I'd prefer a small car.
But if the whole family wants to go somewhere together, a big car would be better, right？
Look. That car seems very expensive. I'm not interested in cars, but I think you probably like it, huh？
I don't think I'll be able to afford it, but it's most guys' dream to have one.
I see. But what matters to me is whether a car can carry my whole family or not.
I see. I'd better keep that in mind, just in case.
Yeah. And the one sitting in your passenger's seat must be Rinko, okay？
...I usually don't get sick or injured, so I've never thought about being hospitalized.
Keeping yourself healthy is the best practice, but you never know what might happen.
You must take care of yourself, okay？ If you get sick, I don't know if I can devote myself to nurse you.
A space alien just walked past us.
What space alien？ It was probably some movie shooting.
I don't know, but it did walk through a wall...
I'm not. Just in case, you must stay close to me, okay？
Did a lion just walk past us...？
But the one I saw was absolutely not a toy or someone wearing a costume！
If it was real, there'd be people running after it trying to catch it, right？
That's true, but... If something happens, you must protect me, okay？
Eh？ I just saw a turtle.
A turtle？ You said you saw a turtle？
Yeah. Well, it might be a giant turtle. And it was walking really fast.
No way. In that case, at least we would see some people around here getting excited to see it.
But I really saw it. Ah, geez. I wonder if I can see it again...
Didn't you see that！？ There was a car-sized cockroach running past us！
Hahaha. Like that kind of cockroach would exist.
It exists！ If it comes back, you must protect me！
Ah... That's... No... It... can't be...
You wouldn't understand if I told you. Anyway, there was a guy who looked like a famous foreign musician...
No, it's impossible for him to be here... Yeah.
Well... Thank you for protecting me.
